Suggested Use: Take 2 capsules twice daily with 8-12oz. of water before or between meals. The first serving is to be taken in the morning, and the second in the afternoon - ideally 30 minutes before a low in energy. Not to be taken in conjunction with hormone-suppressing medications such as Tamoxifen. Consult your healthcare professional before starting Femmenessence if you are taking medication.
